<h1>Difficulty Level Detail</h1>
<h4>(admin-only)</h4>

<a href='<%= difficulty_levels_path %>'>All Difficulty Levels</a>
	| 
<a href='<%= new_difficulty_level_path %>'>New Difficulty Level</a>

